title: Swipe Right in Real Life: Conquering Casual Encounters & Texting Teases (Episode 225)
description:
Show Notes:

Welcome to Swipe Right in Real Life: Conquering Casual Encounters & Texting Teases – this episode of the Inner Confidence Podcast takes daytime approaches and digital follow-ups to a whole new level! We'll teach you how to leave ladies swooning under the sun, and have them giggling at your texts faster than you can say "double-tap". Get ready to become a master of charming sidewalk encounters and sliding into DMs with wit and style. So forget your dating apps, and join us as we explore the art of turning heads and tapping hearts in today's modern world!

01:54 - Uncover the texting mistake you're probably making that's ruining your chances!

04:17 - Discover how following this protocol transformed my clients' dating lives!

10:13 - AD's confession: How he botched his opening lines and learned from it!

14:35 - Clients rate their improvement: Find out how much they've grown!

15:25 - Ditch the pick-up lines you hate! Embrace the ones you'll love!

17:30 - Get the "Lit Up Like a Christmas Tree" reaction from women – here's how!

20:38 - So she has a boyfriend? Don't let that stop you!

21:58 - The secret behind the "fake phone number" line!

28:20 - Why he stopped chasing Instagram follows and what he did instead!

34:12 - "Sorry, I have a boyfriend": Perfect practice opportunities you can't miss!

35:12 - Master the art of approaching women: Think like a chess player!

36:35 - Unveiling the wildest professions of women you'll meet at bars & parties!

38:54 - Good conversation isn't improv – it's all about RECALL!

42:11 - Exposing the inner nice guy: A fake, inauthentic menace!

48:37 - Dating someone with a different first language? Rethink your humor!

52:54 - Scored her number but she ghosted? Let's troubleshoot!

56:37 - Your first text is make or break! Make it count with this tip!

01:01:02 - Clients' game-changing "AHA" moments revealed!

In this episode, we dive into the world of personal development and self-improvement with expert coach, Robbie Kramer. Join us as we explore the power of building inner confidence and leveraging it to achieve success in all areas of life.

To listen to more episodes of the Inner Confidence Podcast, visit the links below:
Website: https://innerconfidence.com/podcast/
iTunes:https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/inner-confidence-podcast/id986699444

RSS: https://innerconfidence.com/series/leverage-podcast/feed/

And if you're interested in learning more about my coaching services and connecting with me, check out these links:
LinkTree: https://linktr.ee/Robbiekramer
Main Site: https://innerconfidence.com/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/robbie_kramer/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@robbie.kramer
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/innerconfidence

Thank you for tuning in, and I look forward to helping you build your inner confidence and achieve success!

Join us : https://innerconfidence.com/leverage/
Book a call with me : https://start.innerconfidence.com/video1
